                var elemHead = a_window.document.getElementsByTagName("head")[0];
                if ( elemHead != null )
                {
                    var elemBase = elemHead.getElementsByTagName("base")[0];
                    if ( elemBase != null && elemBase.getAttribute("target") == "_self")
                        bAvoidSettingTarget = true;

    		}
    		else if (nSplitIndex == 0) {
    			sArgs = a_sUrl;
    		}

    			sPath = arrSplitUrl[0];

    		for (var i = 0; i < arrNameValuePairs.length; ++i) {
    			var nameValuePair = arrNameValuePairs[i];

    	redirectToAngularPage: function (/*object*/a_windowObj, /*string*/a_sBaseURL, /*string*/a_sTarget, /*object*/a_oJsonFormPayload) {

			// Add the form dynamically to the page
    		var frm = a_windowObj.document.createElement("form");

    		for (var i = 0; i < arrNameValueStrings.length; ++i) {
    			var sNameValueString = arrNameValueStrings[i];
